 of the major achievements of "third wave" conservatism in the late twentieth century.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aChristian youthxReligious lifezUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aChristianity and culturezUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aEvangelicalismzUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 0aSuburbszUnited StatesxHistoryy20th century. 4aGeneral. 4aHistory. 4aUnited States. 7aHISTORY / United States / General.2bisacsh1 aLuhr, Eileen, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013z97831106904220 cprintz978052025596840uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/978052094357540uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520943575423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780520943575/original  a978-3-11-069042-2  University of California Press Backlist Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles